'''煤氣燈'''（{{lang-en|gas lamp}}）是[[燈|燈]]一種，通過[[燃燒|燃燒]][[煤氣|煤氣]]進行[[發光|發光]]。'''煤氣燈'''中不一定是[[煤氣|煤氣]]，也可以[[燃燒|燃燒]]其他[[氣體|氣體]]，像是[[氫|氫]]、[[甲烷|甲烷]]、[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]、[[丙烷|丙烷]]、[[丁烷|丁烷]]、[[乙炔|乙炔]]、[[乙烯|乙烯]]、[[天然氣|天然氣]]，或者混合[[氣體|氣體]]。

未有電氣之前，幾普遍使用，可以公用。大城市會街上可見到，[[街燈|街燈]]使用。初時[[煤氣|煤氣]]是[[人|人]]手點著，[[現代|現代]]的[[煤氣|煤氣]][[燈|燈]]有可以自動點著。今日已少見，而轉用[[電燈|電燈]]。

== 歷史 ==
[[春秋戰國|春秋戰國]]時期的中國已經有使用煤氣在家中照明及取暖的紀錄<ref>P. James and N. Thorpe, ''Ancient inventions'' (Michael O Mara Books, 1995), pp. [https://books.google.com/books?id=VmJLd3sSYecC&lpg=PR1&pg=PA427 427] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VmJLd3sSYecC&lpg=PR1&pg=PA427 |date=20201116212347 }}-428: citing [[Chang_Qu|Ch'ang Ch'ü]] (常璩, a geographer), ''[[Chronicles_of_Huayang|Records of the country south of Mount Kua]]'' (華陽國志).</ref>，煤氣以竹筒傳輸，距離可達數英里<ref>{{Cite web |title=Encyclopedia of Environment and Society |last= Robbins |first= Paul  |year=2007 |publisher=Sage Publications|page=1216 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |title=Powering Our Future: An Energy Sourcebook for Sustainable Living |url=https://archive.org/details/poweringourfutur0000smit |last=Smith |first=Kimberly |publisher=Iuniverse Inc. |year=2005 |publication-date=May 31, 2005 |page=[https://archive.org/details/poweringourfutur0000smit/page/56 56]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |title=Power Plays: Energy Options in the Age of Peak Oil |last=Rapier |first=Robert |date=March 30, 2012 |publisher=Apress  |isbn=978-1430240860 |publication-date=March 27, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |title=Investing in Oil and Gas: The ABC's of DPPs (Direct Participation Program)  |last=Heshelow |first=Kathy |publisher=Iuniverse Inc |year=2008 |isbn=978-0595531929 |publication-date=September 2, 2008 |page=52}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |title=A People's History of Science: Miners, Midwives, and Low Mechanicks |last=Conner |first=Clifford |publisher=Nation Books |year=2005 |isbn=978-1560257486 |publication-date=November 8, 2005 |page=[https://archive.org/details/peopleshistoryof0000conn/page/18 18] |url=https://archive.org/details/peopleshistoryof0000conn/page/18 }}</ref>。

在西方，公共照明比煤氣的普及使用早上幾個世紀。1417年，時任[[倫敦市長|倫敦市長]]的{{le|亨利·巴頓|Henry Barton}}爵士規定在冬季晚上掛起燈籠。16世紀初，[[巴黎|巴黎]]居民都要在晚上於面向街道的窗戶傍燃點蠟燭。至1820年，巴黎才開始出現煤氣街燈。

